| colspan=5 | ''Source'': American Heart Association (2003).<ref name="jnc7">{{cite journal |author=Chobanian AV, Bakris GL, Black HR, ''et al.'' |title=Seventh report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Treatment of High Blood Pressure |journal=Hypertension |volume=42 |issue=6 |pages=1206<U+2013>52 |year=2003 |month=December |pmid=14656957 |doi=10.1161/01.HYP.0000107251.49515.c2}}</ref>
